  "overview": "<p>An astonishing animated film by independent creators, made entirely in the free program Blender.</p><p>The film presents a post-apocalyptic world inhabited by both ordinary animals and creatures never seen before. A solitary black cat lives in an abandoned house—until a devastating flood destroys everything around it. Forced to leave its home, the cat sets out in search of a safe place.</p><p>During the journey, we watch as it encounters other inhabitants of this mysterious world.</p><p>Without a single line of dialogue, the film keeps viewers engaged every minute of its runtime.</p>",
